songs.title: Under Satan’s Authority
songs.lyrics:
Now here is something that will stun and very likely outrage many who hear this;
But there is documentary proof that our own Thomas Jefferson and Alexander Hamilton
Became students of Weishaupt...
Jefferson was one of Weishaupt's strongest defenders when he was outlawed by his [ack ack]
And it was Jefferson who infiltrated the Illumin- [ack] into the then newly organized lodges of the "Scottish Rite" in New England.
Here's the proof... In 1789; John Robison warned all Masonic leaders in America that the Illu- [ack] had infiltrated into their lodges...
[Ack][ack] ACK ACK!!
